There is a website for pigeon flyers. It is www.pigeon.org and the results of various races across the country show their results. It worked fine in FF 3.5. Now if you go to pigeon.org>National Database>Race Reports 2011 OB> and click on any of the club results they won't open. They will open in FF 3.5, IE 9, and Chrome. 

Reproducible: Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1.see above

3.

results can't be seen
